"automobiles", "periodicals", "hebdomadaires", "detroit", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-07-18T09:01:19.414Z", "title": "Automotive news", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/77618337/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2005212411/"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1938", "dates": ["[1938 TO 9999]"], "description": ["Weekly, Jan. 8, 2007- Began in June 1938. One issue a year has title: Market data book. At head of title on some issues: Crain. \"The newspaper of the industry.\" Issue for Apr. 24, 1996 also called: American automobile centennial, 1896-1996, v. 1.; Issue no. 5666 (June 26, 1996) also called: American automobile centennial, 1896-1996, v. 2. Vol. 15, no. 2611 (April 6, 1940) (Chronicling America, viewed Sept. 16, 2025). 82nd year, no. 6301 (March 21, 2008) (viewed Sept. 16, 2025)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:36:08.997Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2005212411/", "image_url": [], "index": 33, "language": ["english"], "location": ["united states", "wayne", "detroit", "michigan"], "number": ["42806821", "online resource", "1557-7686", "2005212411", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Crain automotive news"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "automotive news (detroit, mich.;detroit;detroit, mi) 1938-current [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["weekly"], "score": 48.438778, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD TL1 .A865 AN2.M5.D4 A98", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "wayne", "michigan", "automobiles", "periodicals", "hebdomadaires", "detroit", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:41:14.945Z", "title": "Automotive news", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2005212411/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/sn95070373/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/sn95070373", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/c46679b9-b94a-5fd9-b779-c272ac89c04e"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1995", "dates": ["[1995 TO 9999]"], "description": ["Daily Began July 13, 1995. Back issues available online. Print ed.: Detroit news (Detroit, Mich. : 1905). Mode of access: World Wide Web. Description based on: Aug. 18, 1995; title from title screen. Latest issue consulted: 145th year, No. 238 (April 17, 2019) (surrogate)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:34:05.793Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-03", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-03"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/sn95070373/", "image_url": [], "index": 34, "language": ["english"], "location": ["wayne", "michigan", "wayne county", "detroit", "united states"], "number": ["2690-7186", "online resource", "2025-11-07t15:14:20.700000", "sn95070373", "33115544", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "partof": ["catalog", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "the detroit news ([detroit, mich.]) 1995-current [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 34.47525, "shelf_id": "Newspaper", "site": ["usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["newspapers", "wayne", "michigan", "wayne county (mich.)", "periodicals", "detroit (mich.)", "wayne county", "detroit", "electronic journals", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-27T08:50:05.467Z", "title": "The Detroit news", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/sn95070373/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2019201736/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/2019201736", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/a75bc0b9-b4b9-51ec-92f4-ab1f43e513f5"], "campaigns": [], "date": "1858", "dates": ["[1858 TO 9999]"], "description": ["Daily Print began with 1858. Issue for May 10, 1931 called: One hundredth anniversary edition. Editors: Wilbur F. Storey, Aug. 18, 1858-June 4, 1861; Henry N. Walker, June 5-Aug. 27, 1861. Due to strike on Apr. 15, 1962, combined with: Detroit news (Detroit, Mich. : 1905) and called: Detroit news-the Detroit free press. Due to a strike from July 15, 1995-Jan. 1, 1996, combined with: Detroit news (Detroit, Mich. : 1905) and called: Detroit news and free press. Saturday and Sunday issues combined with: Detroit news (Detroit, Mich. : 1905) and called: Detroit news and free press, Dec. 2, 1989-Apr. 30, 2006. Sunday issues include editorial page from Detroit news (Detroit, Mich. : 1905) and called: Sunday free press, May 7, 2006- Issue numbers v. 94, no. 120-v. 94, no. 265 skipped. Suspended Dec. 2, 1955-Jan. 16, 1956; Apr. 12-May 10, 1962; July 14-Nov. 24, 1964; Nov. 18, 1967-Aug. 9, 1968. Saturday and Sunday issues also have numbering for Detroit news. Other daily ed.: Detroit free press (Detroit, Mich. : State ed.). Weekly eds.: Detroit free press (Detroit, Mich. : Weekly), and; Detroit weekly free press; and: Weekly Detroit free press. Regional eds.: Weekly Detroit free press (Detroit, Mich. : Mich. ed.); Semiweekly ed.: Twice-a-week Detroit free press. Description based on: Volume 189, No. 64 (July 7, 2019); title from digital edition caption (freep.com, surrogate provided by publisher, viewed September 24, 2019). Latest issue consulted: Volume 189, No. 64 (July 7, 2019) (viewed September 24, 2019)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:01.189Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-15", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-15"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2019201736/", "image_url": [], "index": 35, "language": ["english"], "location": ["wayne", "michigan", "wayne county", "detroit", "united states"], "number": ["sn97063368", "online resource", "2689-0410", "2019201736", "2025-11-07t12:37:05.400000", "137343179", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Detroit news-the Detroit free press", "Detroit news and free press", "Sunday free press"], "partof": ["directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "catalog", "detroit free press (detroit, mich.;detroit, michigan) 1858-current [online resource]", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["daily"], "score": 34.47525, "shelf_id": "Newspapers", "site": ["usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["newspapers", "wayne", "michigan", "wayne county (mich.)", "periodicals", "detroit (mich.)", "wayne county", "detroit", "electronic journals", "united states"], "timestamp": "2026-05-26T20:57:39.303Z", "title": "Detroit free press", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/2019201736/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/42047197/", "http://lccn.loc.gov/42047197", "https://search.catalog.loc.gov/instances/1cb41eab-f4f4-594f-9504-a534e4b741bf"], "batch": ["mimtptc_dexter_ver01"], "campaigns": [], "contributor": ["international union, united automobile workers of america (a.f. of l.)", "international union, united automobile workers of america (cio)", "international union, united automobile, aircraft, and agricultural implement workers of america"], "date": "1936", "description": ["Semimonthly, <1944-> Began with v. 1 in June 1936. -v. 20, no. 12 (Dec. 1957). Affiliated with: American Federation of Labor, <July 7, 1936>-Oct. 1936; Congress of Industrial Organizations, Nov. 1936-Dec. 1957. Edited: -Jan. 7, 1939 by H. Martin; Jan. 14, 1939- by the International Executive Board. Preceded by a \"Special convention number\" dated May 1936. Includes separately paged special issues. Archived issues are available in digital format from the Library of Congress Chronicling America online collection. Official publication of: 1936-<1940> International Union, United Automobile Workers of America; <1944>-1957 International Union, United Automobile, Aircraft, and Agricultural Implement Workers of America. Description based on surrogate of: Vol. 1, no. 2 (July 7, 1936); title from caption. Solidarity (Detroit, Mich.) 0164-856X (DLC)sn 78001402 (OCoLC)4309031"], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-06-05T18:25:08.284Z", "group": ["newspaper-titles", "ndnp/newspapers", "catalog-split-02", "catalog", "united-states-newspaper-directory", "main-catalog-split-02"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/42047197/", "image_url": [], "index": 36, "language": ["english"], "latlong": [42.3329407, -83.0478365], "location": ["united states", "wayne", "detroit", "michigan"], "location_str": "", "lonlat": [-83.0478365, 42.3329407], "number": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/42047197/1936-05-01/ed-1/", "sn78001402", "2268881", "online resource", "http://www.loc.gov/item/42047197/1951-02-01/ed-1/", "404", "1", "sn94023201", "42047197", "2024-01-10t18:39:57.321128", "2025-09-22t14:01:06.500000", "2769-3201", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["United worker", "Automobile united worker"], "partof": ["united automobile worker (detroit, mich.) 1936-1957", "catalog", "chronicling america", "serial and government publications division", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries"], "publication_frequency": ["semimonthly"], "score": 34.47525, "shelf_id": "HD6350.A8 U6", "site": ["chroniclingamerica", "usnd", "catalog"], "subject": ["wayne", "michigan", "automobile industry workers", "periodicals", "labor unions", "international union, united automobile workers of america (cio)", "labor movement", "detroit", "automobile industry and trade", "united states", "international union, united automobile, aircraft, and agricultural implement workers of america"], "timestamp": "2026-07-18T09:01:19.414Z", "title": "United automobile worker", "type": ["title"], "url": "https://www.loc.gov/item/42047197/"}, {"access_restricted": false, "aka": ["http://www.loc.gov/item/2018270596/"], "campaigns": [], "contributor": ["south slavic socialist labor party federation", "slepcevich, peter", "petrovich, lazar"], "date": "1907", "dates": ["[1907 TO 1970]"], "description": ["Semimonthly, July 14, 1966-1970 Began with Sept. 19, 1907 issue; ceased Oct. 8, 1970. Imprint varies: 1907-1910 published in New York; 1910-1943 published in Cleveland; 1943-1970 published in Detroit. Editors: Lazar Petrovich, <1919>-1926, 1948-1957; Peter Slepcevich, <1958-1967>. Also issued on microfilm from the Library of Congress Photoduplication Service and the New York Public Library. In Serbo-Croatian (Roman) with some columns in English. Official organ of the: South Slavic Socialist Labor Party Federation. Description based on: Vol. XXXIV, No. 3 (January 16, 1941); title from masthead (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed December 19, 2018). Latest issue consulted: Vol. XXXIX, No. 3 (January 17, 1946) (Chroniclingamerica.loc.gov, viewed December 19, 2018)."], "digitized": true, "extract_timestamp": "2026-05-19T21:37:46.349Z", "group": ["ndnp/newspapers", "united-states-newspaper-directory"], "hassegments": false, "id": "http://www.loc.gov/item/2018270596/", "image_url": [], "index": 37, "language": ["english", "croatian"], "location": ["wayne", "michigan", "cuyahoga", "new york", "detroit", "ohio", "united states", "cleveland", "new york city"], "number": ["1079422283", "2018270596", "online resource", "2641-0168", "2026-04-13t21:30:13"], "original_format": ["newspaper"], "other_title": ["Workers' struggle"], "partof": ["radni\u010dka borba = workers' struggle (cleveland, o.) 1907-1970 [online resource]", "directory of u.s. newspapers in american libraries", "serial and government publications division"], "publication_frequency": ["semimonthly"], "score": 32.1619, "shelf_id": "ISSN RECORD", "site": ["usnd"], "subject": ["newspapers", "wayne", "michigan", "new york (state)", "cuyahoga", "new york (n.y.)", "cleveland (ohio)", "detroit (mich.)", "new york", "yugoslavian", "yugoslavs", "detroit", "ohio", "united states", "cleveland"], "timest